.TH man_3_printf "26 October 2020" "0.32" "_printf man page"
.SH NAME
.B_printf - format and print data
.SH SYNOPSIS

_printf FORMAT [ARGUMENT] ...
_printf OPTION

.SH DESCRIPTION
The function _printf produces output according to a format or executes accodring to option.  The functions _printf() and vprintf() write output to stdout,
the standard output stream.

FORMAT controls the output as in C printf. The following are th format specifiers used.

--help
display this help and exit
--version
output version information and exit

%      format specifier when used in combination with different characters as seen below.

%c     character type

%s     string type

%%     % character

%d     signed integer

%i     signed integer

.SH SEE ALSO
printf(3)
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
